<hr size=1> First things first. Congratulations upon your succesfull raid on Fear. Congratulations to those that walked home with new armour, items, weapons, and victory. I Salute your strength and will.<br>
<br>
Now, on to business. <br>
<br>
I am seeking approval of the Triad for a chance to be given a sponsor in an attempt to become a qualified member of Violent Harvest. You see before you the bright pallid flesh of a Feir'Dal. <br>
<br>
Do not fall victim to this trick.<br>
<br>
I am Shintenshi Kurayami. I was raised by the foolish Feir'Dal and taught their secrets, yet within me beats the heart of Our Dark Prince.<br>
<br>
Do not be fooled.<br>
<br>
I am not good. I am not evil. I do not title myself or my actions by such foolhardy titles. <br>
<br>
I am justified.<br>
<br>
You seek to harvest the souls of Norrath and give them unto Our Dark Prince. So be it. I shall follow the path you lay out before me. Your means are my goals. I seek to administer the destruction and chaos you long to see befall the settlers of this rock. <br>
<br>
So be it.<br>
<br>
Give me a quest.<br>
<br>
Give me an enemy.<br>
<br>
Give me a chance.<br>
<br>
I shall give you a victory.<br>
           <br>
          ~Shin<br>
