<br>
&quot;Interesting words. An interesting offer. But you are in no position to demand such things from your superiors. Better you kneel and beg atonement, light born.&quot;<br>
<br>
He stops his pacing, standing just before the Koada'Dal, his violet eyes blazing with a intense and feral edged light. &quot;Your face... It seems very familiar. We crossed blades just outside Kelethin, did we not? If you are the one I remember I would be interested in talking more.&quot;<br>
<br>
Shaking his head he turns away, &quot;If the Triad even chooses to speak to you, you will have much to prove. I do not know if such a thing can be done. Stride carefully in these halls, most are not so forgiving as I.&quot; <p><center><a href="http://www.violentharvest.com"><img src="http://home.columbus.rr.com/harvest/khas_sig.jpg"></a><br>
